text: Robert Garrett (1875–1961) was an American athlete. Robert Garrett may also refer to: * Bobby Garrett (1932–1987), American football player * Bob Garrett (TV), character on the TV series October Road * Robert Garrett (footballer) (born 1988), Northern Irish footballer * Robert Garrett (basketball) (born 1977), German basketball player * Robert Garrett (British Army officer) (1794–1869)
title: Robert Garrett (disambiguation)
